## Soft badges

The style of soft badges was updated prior to the Dark Mode work. Instead of using a white background, badges now use their respective “faint” tint.

#### Rationale:

This change serves two purposes:

1. It aligns messaging badges with the messaging design system.
1. It visually differentiates badges from soft buttons.

For example, hero and primary badges were previously identical to hero and primary soft buttons, which caused confusion.Again, this is not a new variation but a refinement of the existing style.

**Note:** The Neutral badge style has been removed.

