## Switch

The colour of the switch component has been modified so it functions correctly in Dark Mode without the need for a bespoke component-specific token. The updated design now uses two colours instead of three, and the drop shadow has been removed.

#### Rationale:

The current white switch handle is not accessible, as it has no border and relies on a drop shadow for separation.

