## Close icons

There are currently inconsistencies with the close icons – some are muted, some are primary, some use a hover state and others do not. To resolve this the close icons used in Modals, Bottom Sheets, and Popovers are now red and no longer include hover states.

#### Rationale:

This provides better consistency and aligns with the mobile banking app.

